### 上传影像（带FormData）
POST http://localhost:8000/images/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image_name"

小明图
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="resolution"

1m
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="capture_date"

2025-03-03
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="satellite"

swot
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="type"

dom
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="region_code"

320612001
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image_file"; filename="test_image.tif"
Content-Type: image/tiff

< ./path/to/your/image.tif
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="shp_files"; filename="boundary.shp"
Content-Type: application/octet-stream

< ./path/to/your/boundary.shp
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="shp_files"; filename="boundary.dbf"
Content-Type: application/octet-stream

< ./path/to/your/boundary.dbf
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="shp_files"; filename="boundary.prj"
Content-Type: application/octet-stream

< ./path/to/your/boundary.prj
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### 获取所有影像列表
GET http://localhost:8000/images/list

### 根据ID获取影像
GET http://localhost:8000/images/1

